# Sheba Cup Coffee — Navigation

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root for the full codebase index.

## Where to edit common features

| Feature | Primary files |
|---------|----------------|
| Home page | `app/[lang]/(client)/page.tsx`, `components/ProductGrid.tsx`, `components/ShopFeatures.tsx` |
| Shop / filters | `components/shopPage/Shop.tsx`, `components/shopPage/CategoryList.tsx` |
| Wholesale form | `components/shopPage/ShopWholesaleSection.tsx`, `app/api/wholesalers/route.ts` |
| Nav / header | `constants/index.ts`, `components/layout/HeaderMenu.tsx`, `components/Header.tsx` |
| Product detail | `components/ProductContent.tsx`, `components/product/` |
| i18n copy | `dictionaries/en.json`, `lib/dictionary.ts`, `i18n-config.ts` |
| CMS content | `sanity/schemaTypes/`, `sanity/queries/` |
| Auth / middleware | `proxy.ts` |
| Checkout / Stripe | `components/checkout/`, `app/api/checkout/stripe/route.ts` |

## Stack reminders

- Next.js 16 App Router, locales: `en`, `es`, `ar` only
- Path alias: `@/` → repo root
- Package manager: **npm** (use `package-lock.json`, not pnpm)
